item.title: More spawning help please
item.dc:creator: @i_rc_and_wc i rc and wc
item.description:
@i_rc_and_wc wrote:

On your Moparscape window there should be a ‘Help’ tab. Click it scroll down to Item ID’s then search the item you’re looking for.

PS.
The code for it is

::pickup (the number from ur code) 10 – for the 10 part you can change it for money.

IE ((money code)) ::pickup 0995 1000000. And it’d give you 10M. You can go upto 999M but you have to type in 1B because you can’t change the 10 after the code.
